Package com.bws.jdistil.core.process.model

Class FilterCriteriaDefinition

java.lang.Object
com.bws.jdistil.core.process.model.FilterCriteriaDefinition
public class FilterCriteriaDefinition extends Object
Creates a filter criteria object using parameter data contained in a given HTTP request and predefined value criterion definitions and order criteria definitions.
